    "And if that's the case, your attention allocation fails to fulfill your special duties of friendship.",
    "12 Now, we don't want to overstate this point.",
    "We humans are cognitively and morally frail creatures who often fail to attend appropriately to the people and things most dear to us even under favorable circumstances.",
    "Nonetheless, the morally significant bonds we share with others demand some robustness.",
    "If you all but forget that your depressed friend exists when she disappears from your social media feeds, this is at least morally suboptimal."
